I’m about to turn 14, so i decided to have a little get together with some friends of mine. even though we all go to school together, some of us had never even met each other! we went bowling and ended up at sophie’s house and made some tiktoks. over the past month, i’ve gotten really close to these people and i’m glad that they’re in my life! i love them bunches 🥰!

january 2019 - december 2019. it feels so weird to say it’s officially 2020 but it’s true! with my birthday coming up soon and having to go back to school afterwards is kind of weird. i’m about to be 14 years old! i wonder what this decade is gonna bring to us. -

tl;dr: I went to All-Region, freaked out, but made it. -
If many of you don’t know, I attended my first ever All-Region Audition ever! I was very nervous and maybe (definitely) choked a little bit. After doing my audition, i felt better about it and tried to keep a positive attitude.  Oh boy did that help because I made it! 2nd Band Last Chair (12) may be bad but as long as I get to experience something like this, I’ll take whatever I can get. -
